1
00:00:03,270 --> 00:00:08,370
... and run interference for your girl
on the dance floor.

2
00:00:08,420 --> 00:00:12,160
I fronted the piano in there every night
from 8:00 until the place closed up ...

3
00:00:12,210 --> 00:00:14,370
... which usually meant 4:00 in the morning.

4
00:00:14,420 --> 00:00:18,570
A good job, as jobs went in those days.

5
00:00:20,200 --> 00:00:22,090
And then too ...

6
00:00:22,140 --> 00:00:23,620
... there was Sue.

7
00:00:23,670 --> 00:00:27,060
... who made working there a little like working in heaven.

8
00:00:27,110 --> 00:00:31,560
But how we felt about each other.
Well, there was nothing very unusual in that.

9
00:00:31,610 --> 00:00:34,590
I was an ordinary healthy guy,
and she was an ordinary healthy girl.

10
00:00:34,640 --> 00:00:38,050
And when you add those two together,
you get an ordinary healthy romance.

11
00:00:38,100 --> 00:00:39,950
Which is the old story ...

12
00:00:40,000 --> 00:00:42,290
... sure, but somehow ...

13
00:00:42,340 --> 00:00:46,650
... the most wonderful thing in the world.

14
00:00:52,080 --> 00:00:56,170
All in all, I was a pretty lucky guy.

15
00:01:07,280 --> 00:01:09,330
Mr Paderewsky, I presume ...

16
00:01:09,380 --> 00:01:10,350
It's beautiful.

17
00:01:10,400 --> 00:01:12,590
You re going to make Carnegie Hall your door.

18
00:01:12,640 --> 00:01:15,260
Yeah, as a janitor.

19
00:01:15,310 --> 00:01:17,100
I ll make my debut in the basement.

20
00:01:17,150 --> 00:01:19,260
I don t blame you for being bitter, darling but ...

21
00:01:19,310 --> 00:01:20,920
... you mustn t give up hope.

22
00:01:20,970 --> 00:01:22,790
- Why, some day ...
- Yeah, some day ...

23
00:01:22,840 --> 00:01:24,390
... if I don t get arthritis first.

24
00:01:24,440 --> 00:01:28,530
In the meantime, let s blow this trap.

25
00:01:46,200 --> 00:01:48,630
- Like to get something to eat, hon ?
- I don t think so, Al.

26
00:01:48,680 --> 00:01:51,810
I lose my appetite working in this fleabag.

27
00:01:51,860 --> 00:01:54,660
- Let's go home.
- OK.

28
00:01:54,710 --> 00:01:57,330
I can t stand much more of that dump.

29
00:01:57,380 --> 00:02:00,010
Did you see that drunk tonight trying to paw me.

30
00:02:00,060 --> 00:02:01,210
No, what drunk?

31
00:02:01,260 --> 00:02:04,330
It doesn t matter what drunk!

